columns.name: name
columns.description: The friendly name that identifies the subnet.

columns.name: id
columns.description: Contains ID to identify a subnet uniquely.

columns.name: virtual_network_name
columns.description: The friendly name of the virtual network in which the subnet is created.

columns.name: etag
columns.description: An unique read-only string that changes whenever the resource is updated.

columns.name: provisioning_state
columns.description: The provisioning state of the subnet resource.

columns.name: address_prefix
columns.description: Contains the address prefix for the subnet.

columns.name: nat_gateway_id
columns.description: The ID of the Nat gateway associated with the subnet.

columns.name: network_security_group_id
columns.description: Network security group associated with the subnet.

columns.name: private_endpoint_network_policies
columns.description: Enable or Disable apply network policies on private end point in the subnet.

columns.name: private_link_service_network_policies
columns.description: Enable or Disable apply network policies on private link service in the subnet.

columns.name: route_table_id
columns.description: Route table associated with the subnet.

columns.name: delegations
columns.description: A list of references to the delegations on the subnet.

columns.name: ip_configurations
columns.description: IP Configuration details in a subnet.

columns.name: service_endpoint_policies
columns.description: A list of service endpoint policies.
